Title: Mack is from Mars, Sione's a Psycho
Plot:
When Mack sees how bad the St Cardinal?s netball team is, he decides they need help from an expert, disguises himself as a Muslim, and impresses the girls with his excellent skills!

Mack discovers the joys of female company and becomes frustrated with his monosyllabic mates. The story is further complicated when Sione falls for a mysterious stranger
